            <description><![CDATA[【五洲之约·青春共融】第五届国际文化嘉年华5月18日即将盛大启航]]></description>
            <link>https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/05/15/121757</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="true">https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/05/15/121757</guid>
            <pubDate>Thu, 15 May 2025 13:55:57 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded>&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;五洲之约&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;·青春共融&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;One World, One Campus&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;哈尔滨工业大学第五届国际文化嘉年华即将于&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;5&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;月&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;18&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;日盛大启航&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;The 5th International Cultural Carnival of Harbin Institute of Technology is coming on May&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;18th&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;跨越山海，相聚工大&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;Across Mountains and Seas, We Gather at HIT&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;值此建校&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;105&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;周年之际，哈尔滨工业大学携手世界学子、生源国领事及国内兄弟高校，共聚丁香校园，共享多元文化。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;105&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;个特色展位荟萃各国风情、非遗技艺与教育成果，&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;40&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;余场精彩表演演绎五洲艺术魅力，更有&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;留学龙江&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;国情教育实践基地联合体启幕在即。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;5&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;月&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;18&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;日上午&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;10:30&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;，让我们在美食、音乐与对话中，共绘&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;&quot;One World, One Campus&quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;的文明互鉴新图景！&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;On the occasion of the 105th anniversary, Harbin Institute of Technology invites students worldwide , consuls from main student source countries, and other universities in China to come together on its lilac-adorned campus and celebrate the cultural carnival. With&amp;nbsp;105 unique booths&amp;nbsp;showcasing global traditions, intangible cultural heritage, and educational achievements, along with&amp;nbsp;over 40 spectacular performances&amp;nbsp;highlighting the artistic charm of five continents, the event will also witness the launch of the&amp;nbsp;&quot;Study in Heilongjiang&quot; National Education Practice Base Consortium. At&amp;nbsp;10:30 AM on May 18th, let us join in the festivities of food, music, and dialogue to co-create a new vision of cultural exchange under the theme&amp;nbsp;&quot;One World, One Campus&quot;!&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;活动时间：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;2025&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;年&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;5&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;月&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;18&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;日（星期日）&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;10:30-15:30&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;Event Time:&amp;nbsp;May 18, 2025 (Sunday), 10:30 AM &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;– &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;3:30 PM&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;活动地点：一校区司令街&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;Event Location:&amp;nbsp;Siling Street, Main Campus&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;精彩节目预告&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;Program Schedule Preview&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;国际学生舞蹈表演《万疆》&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;——异域风采与中国歌曲交相辉映&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;Dance: Boundless Homeland &amp;nbsp;Performed by: International Students&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;京剧《捉放曹》选段&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;——哈工大京剧社倾情呈现国粹经典&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;Beijing Opera Zhuo Fang Cao &amp;nbsp;Performed by: HIT Beijing Opera Group&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;摩洛哥风情歌舞秀&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;——摩洛哥特色歌舞与时尚走秀&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;Music and Model Show &amp;nbsp;Performed by: Moroccan Students&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;泰国学子歌曲串烧&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;——从泰国传统歌曲到中文金曲《逆光》&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;Music Show &amp;nbsp;Performed by: Thailand Students&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;多国学生合唱《明天会更好》&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;——青春之声唱响美好未来&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;Choral Performance Tomorrow will be better&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;right&quot; style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;国际教育学院&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;right&quot; style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;2025&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;年&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;5&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;月&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Calibri&quot;&gt;15&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;宋体&quot;&gt;日&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

